Subject: Server Access Error || Satcom Infotech || || Internal Server ||
Description: Dear Team, We are unable to access our EPP server console and getting the below error while accessing the EPP console access. Oops! An Error Occurred The server returned a "500 Internal Server Error". Something is broken Please e-mail us at support@endpointprotector.com and let us know what you were doing when this error occurred. We will fix it as soon as possible. Sorry for any inconvenience caused. Regards, Prasanth
Solution_Comment__c:
Mysql service was running and did not start even with recovery.
Removed iblogfile and the service started. After server restart the service was still running.
